Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:47.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I should talk to Sachiko-sama about Touko-chan running away from home?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:50.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi, Mass is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.06,0:01:54.18,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:05.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Bye! Have a good New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:08.40,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:10.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes. You can do it very neatly this way. {Missing line - sleepy Bunnie}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.24,0:02:12.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.41,0:02:17.71,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Shimako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:20.17,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're challenging yourself by making cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:21.25,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:23.75,Marimite,,0,0,0,,For some reason, I just wanted to make one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.09,0:02:25.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:28.05,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Rei-sama said she would teach me if I was going to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.26,0:02:31.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:35.68,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We can't eat Rei-sama's special cake next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:38.77,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Shimako-san wanted to continue what she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:43.27,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We're going to start feeling the approach of the graduation ceremony like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.57,0:02:48.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for being late!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:51.99,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Ah, Yumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.57,0:02:54.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I apologize for this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:02:57.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Nope. I'm sorry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:02:59.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko-chan, are you by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:01.50,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Kanako-san and Touko will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:05.42,Marimite,,0,0,0,,They met Rosa Chinensis on their way here, so they left this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:08.17,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I was told to carry this over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:12.13,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's Youko-sama's writing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:15.05,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She was the previous Rosa Chinensis, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:16.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes, she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:22.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Kanako and Touko are coming in a bit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:24.19,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:29.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That Yoshino...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:37.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yoshino is also going to use today's party as a chance to introduce her candidate for sisterhood to Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:40.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Would you like help me put these up together?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:41.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:51.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sorry we're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:52.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:56.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Kanako-chan. Touko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:04:00.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama, thank you for inviting us today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:10.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:12.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the invitation again this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:14.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sorry for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:16.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Am I the last one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:20.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I guess not. Yoshino-san isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:22.37,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:24.37,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:26.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:32.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:34.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:37.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Rei-sama's nervous from having to meet Yoshino's candidate,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:42.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,and Yoshino-san froze after seeing Rei-sama's nervousness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:45.10,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That girl is Nana-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:47.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Do your best, Yoshino-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:52.48,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then how about we take a group picture first?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:53.24,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:56.20,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Can everyone please line up in two rows over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:00.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Just what I expected from you, Tsutako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:03.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You changed the atmosphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:08.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan, scoot in a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:09.34,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:11.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:12.17,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:14.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,For coming even though you had plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:19.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But I didn't think it was like me to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:22.06,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It is different from your usual character, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:26.27,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm taking it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:30.69,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Okay! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:34.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then how about we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.15,0:05:36.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We'll decide the seating arrangement by drawing lots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:38.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Drawing lots?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:45.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yoshino-san looks crestfallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:47.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She couldn't sit next to Arima Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.96,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm also separated from Touko-chan as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:53.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I really want to switch seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:58.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Let's start with a simple self-introduction and a report on how you've been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:03.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since we've all gathered like this, right Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:01.55,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,A self-introduction during something like this? {while}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:05.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The last time was the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:06.98,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,I see! It's for Arima Nana-san's sake! {while}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:06.98,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sounds fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:11.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Second year, pine class. Takeshima Tsutako.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:13.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm a member of the photography club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:17.86,Marimite,,0,0,0,,To conclude my self-introduction, I'm hoping to become a photographer in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:20.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'll make it so no one will feel down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:28.50,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm the Rosa Gigantea en bouton, Nijo Noriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:30.67,Marimite,,0,0,0,,My hobby is appreciating Buddhist statuary art.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:35.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I wanted to take a small trip to view some Buddhist statues after exams,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:37.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,but I'm no longer able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:46.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm Rosa Foetida, Hasekura Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:51.40,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm a member of the kendo club. However, we've only been truly busy this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:55.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there anything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.73,0:06:56.82,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:07:00.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Due to some unexpected events recently, I now have a boyfriend who's younger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:08.58,Marimite,,0,0,0,,How old is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:11.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,About ten?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:12.37,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Ten?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:15.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:17.84,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touch! {TL Note: This is similar to the English word "tag".}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.92,tlnote,,0,0,0,,TL Note: This is similar to the English word "tag".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.47,0:07:26.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Second year, pine class. Fukuzawa Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:28.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm the Rosa Chinensis en bouton.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:29.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:33.40,Marimite,,0,0,0,,During the break, I went to an amusement park with Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:39.11,Marimite,,0,0,0,,On the way back, we stopped by her house and I had a taste of her mother's delicious homemade mille-feuille.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.69,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:51.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Middle school division third year, Arima Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:54.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thank you for inviting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:56.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Due to some unexpected events,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:08:01.09,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I came to know of Shimazu Yoshino-sama and I heard about the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:04.34,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I absolutely wanted to attend this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:08.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Although I realize it's rude of me to have requested of such a thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:11.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I still would like to ask for everyone's guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:20.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,After that, Onee-sama talked about what happened at the amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:24.11,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Kanako-chan reported to us that she joined the basketball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:29.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Shimako-san talked about how she came to have an interest in making sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:31.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And then finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:36.71,Marimite,,0,0,0,,First year, camellia class. Matsudaira Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:38.29,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm a member of the drama club.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:41.01,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:53.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Young master, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:07.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh, you were providing for the needy in accordance with practice on this holy night, were you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:10.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:14.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Young master, what a kind person you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:22.17,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I got it! It's a small monologue!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:24.09,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:27.68,Marimite,,0,0,0,,My clothes are tattered, and I'm also always hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:29.72,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Of course I would be mistaken for a pitiful child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:45.82,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Was that okay, Kanako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:52.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I had nothing particularly to mention, so that was a substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:05.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Just in that small amount of time, she was able to grab everyone's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:09.34,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan really is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:17.48,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It has the same taste as Rei-sama's!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:21.94,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The Bûche de Noël that Rei-sama and Shimako-san made was really delicious. {TL Note: Bûche de Noël is known as a yule log in English.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:21.94,tlnote,,0,0,0,,TL Note: Bûche de Noël is known as a yule log in English.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:26.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, it was free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:30.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We played games together and talked to each other. We passed the time happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:43.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If you're looking for Kanako-chan, she already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:46.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She said she was going to meet with her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:52.80,Marimite,,0,0,0,,In order to maintain the joyful atmosphere, she said she would sneak out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:56.06,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She didn't want Touko-chan to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:11:01.02,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:03.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Let's play the next game!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:10.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko-chan, ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:12.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko-chan, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:19.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Wait, Shimako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:25.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:30.13,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She asked me if I was going to inherit my family's line of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:31.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We run a temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:34.89,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And then what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:41.89,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I said I didn't know, and then she asked me what would happen to the temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.89,0:11:43.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:46.86,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Who knows? It'd be nice if my brother would inherit it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:49.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Shimako-san, you have an older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:50.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:54.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan said the same thing, and then she seemed like she was contemplating something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:58.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I wonder if something happened with Touko-chan's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:00.16,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Something probably did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:02.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She won't come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.54,0:12:06.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If it's you, Yumi-san, she'll listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:10.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Don't be too hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:12.01,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:19.39,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why am I the only one that doesn't know that about you, Rei-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:27.11,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:31.94,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yoshino-san brought Nana-san over to Rosa Foetida, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:33.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Rei-chan! Rei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:38.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Nana-san said that she wanted to meet you someday. {This wasnt TLed all the way. I think it says this - Seto}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:40.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Okay. Bring her to my place during winter break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:42.96,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We don't have to rush it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:47.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,How about when you visit in the spring to help the underclassmen? {TL Note: The school year ends and begins in the spring in Japan, so Rei will have already graduated by then.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:49.04,tlnote,,0,0,0,,TL Note: The school year ends and begins in the spring in Japan, so Rei will have already graduated by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:49.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I won't be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:53.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But the Lilian Women's College is nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.84,0:12:56.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I didn't send in my application for admissions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:12:58.80,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:04.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to the college here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.48,0:13:08.27,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sachiko-sama, Rei-chan is....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:10.77,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yoshino-chan, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:15.86,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sachiko-sama, you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:20.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:22.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Because you didn't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:27.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Of course I wouldn't ask! You always told me you were going to Lilian!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:30.09,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're right. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:33.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why are you going to a different university?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.63,0:13:36.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I want to study a subject that's not offered at Lilian.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:38.80,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:42.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of studying physical education.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:48.81,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'll inherit it or not, but I want to stay involved with my family's dojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:54.40,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's also useful to have knowledge of the body's functions and how it moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:57.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Most importantly, it's what I want to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.62,0:14:06.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I wish I could've heard that from you when we were alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:10.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If you had just told me straightforwardly, I wouldn't be so against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:12.25,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:14.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I wanted to know before anyone else did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:16.84,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:24.72,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:28.19,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What do you plan to do after graduation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.14,0:14:35.44,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I wanted to talk about this elsewhere, when it's just the two of us.{timing?? - tired Bunnie}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:37.61,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:41.99,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'll be going to Lilian Women's College.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:43.70,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:47.16,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.83,0:14:51.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong with me being nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:53.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Ah, no! That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:54.71,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:59.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,How silly. I submitted my application, but the results haven't come out yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:04.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved! I won't be separated from Onee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.73,0:15:12.40,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's right! Before I forget, I have to give her my present.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:25.37,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:28.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:29.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:32.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You said it was fine if I left in the middle of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:35.17,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I wasn't even aware that Kanako-chan left already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:40.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why are you coming with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.97,0:15:45.01,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I just felt like walking with you for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:48.27,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Without being considerate of how I feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:49.39,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Am I a bother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:52.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:03.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Did you really only feel like walking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:07.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I thought you might want to talk about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:09.70,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Ah, something to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:12.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:15.42,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Rei-sama's decision was surprising, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:17.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She's going to a different university.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:20.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sachiko-sama will be staying here at Lilian,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:22.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,so you're happy, aren't you, Yumi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:31.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Well, basically, third years are all facing the dreams they have for themselves and heading straight for them, or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.73,0:16:35.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No one can achieve the same future that they've framed in their mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:38.19,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:43.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:48.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,When we were in primary school, we were given a blank map during social studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:53.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,At the time, I became really excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:59.09,Marimite,,0,0,0,,"I'll draw mountains and cities here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:04.72,Marimite,,0,0,0,,A perfect map that looks almost printed, and wouldn't lose to anything else."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:10.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But then I realized,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:13.39,Marimite,,0,0,0,,it's not that easy to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:20.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The page that I had drawn was completely different from what I had imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.78,0:17:26.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even a single blank atlas can't go that well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:29.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's the same with life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:30.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I had my eyes opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:37.75,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If you can't make a perfect map, it would've been better to just make the map a wet mess of pink flowers and water dots!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:42.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If I did that, I might have made a beautiful map for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:43.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:45.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do it. {missing line? - by Bunnie}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:47.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:51.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I've been ranting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:53.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Please forget what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:03.82,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:20.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:24.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,become my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:32.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Am I not good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:34.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:52.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,"Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:55.70,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama, what a kind person you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:18:58.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Just joking."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:01.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And if I said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:08.01,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm not a good girl like the one in the monologue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:11.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If this is charity for the sake of this holy night, go somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.64,0:19:12.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:15.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I cannot accept your rosary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:16.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:41.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:43.29,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.29,0:19:46.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I thought that if I waited here, we could be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:54.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's a handkerchief, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:56.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Open it and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:19:59.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Don't think that it's as poorly made as last year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:03.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I've improved this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:08.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Roses. Red roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:11.99,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:14.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's right, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:27.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:28.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,A book cover. {... Am I mishearing things?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:32.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This is a rose, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.93,0:20:36.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We were thinking of the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:38.10,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.60,0:20:40.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'll use it during both winter and summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.65,0:20:46.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:43.48,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's hot during summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:50.11,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:54.99,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Did something happen with Touko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:02.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She didn't accept my rosary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:06.96,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.71,0:21:10.42,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan isn't the only first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:11.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:14.09,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.18,0:21:18.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then you just can't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.39,0:21:26.40,Marimite,,0,0,0,,When Shimako refused me, I thought that it didn't have to be Shimako.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:30.19,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But it was different from when you rejected me, Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.19,0:21:33.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even if I would be too stubborn, I wanted you to accept my rosary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:38.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Having your rosary refused isn't the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.08,0:21:41.58,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Be more confident. {missing line maybe? - Bunnie}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:42.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.33,0:21:49.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But, it's painful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:50.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:21:59.05,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.22,0:22:03.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then, is it alright if I cry a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.89,0:22:05.06,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.76,0:24:10.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,My parents mentioned annulling the engagement between Suguru-san and I during this New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.27,0:24:13.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's fine, right? Both of you are still young, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.90,0:24:17.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But weren't you going to make us marry, and then entrust the Ogasawara group to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.90,0:24:22.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh? The reason we had the two of you get engaged was because you had said that you wanted to be Suguru-san's wife when you were a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.95,0:24:27.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That determination to jump off the platform at Kiyomizu was easily destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.95,0:24:28.95,tlnoteright,,0,0,0,,TL Note: Kiyomizu Temple is a temple in Kyoto that is very famous for its incredibly high platform. This is just a reference to having the "courage" to jump off the platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.45,0:24:30.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Next time, The Other Side of the Clouded Glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.08,0:24:32.96,Marimite,,0,0,0,,New Years actually had a story like this.
