Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.51,0:22:51.61,englished,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)}Somehow, despite the colors of the city, the lonely winter scenery
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.61,0:22:59.32,englished,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)}makes me think of when you showed your back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.07,0:23:08.04,englished,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)}Between the two of us is a transparent wall
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.04,0:23:17.55,englished,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)}which is turning foggy with my crystallized sighs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.05,0:23:27.85,englished,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)}Window glass, window glass, so obscure that I cannot see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:34.06,englished,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)}even though I know that you're right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:44.03,englished,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)}Whether you're laughing, or crying, show me your face.
